    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s M-Division engineering, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system. The vehicle exhibits flawless mechanical synchronicity, with a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission delivering precise gate entry and a mechanical limited-slip differential providing optimal torque distribution. The chassis is in showroom condition, featuring a documented preventative subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that remains tight and responsive. Every component, from the factory-spec bushings to the pristine cooling system, reflects a rigorous maintenance protocol. This is a concourse-level specimen for the purist who values structural integrity and peak atmospheric performance.",
